{
  "texts": [
    "The system employs advanced models, Open Pose [4] and Dense Pose [31], which are integral parts of the preprocessing pipeline.",
    "These models extract detailed pose maps that identify key body landmarks, such as joints and limbs, ensuring an accurate representation of the user's anatomy, regardless of how dynamic or complex their pose may be.",
    "A crucial component of FITMI is the geometric matching module utilized during the garment fitting process.",
    "This module computes a correlation map between the user's body and the in-shop garment.",
    "By identifying how the garment should be adjusted to align with the user's unique body shape and pose, it employs a Thin-Plate Spline (TPS) transformation [8]."
  ]
}